CROCO - Catalyst Room Control System
===============================================================================

Copyright (C) Catalyst Event Production Services 2013
All Rights Reserved

* HAL:   The HAL subsystem is responsible for communicating with distributed
         hardware devices, anything from GPIO devices to audio routers.

* EXECUTIVE:  The executive contains the logic for operating the programmed
              system.
              
* UI:    The UI is responsible for interacting with the system - whether it's
         via touch-screen, mobile device or tablet.

* SITE-SPEC: The site-specific directory is for site-specific configuration for
             deployments of the CROCO system.

